<body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100">
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <nav class="navbar bg-white" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #EEEEEE;">
      <div class="container">
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
          <li><a href="/category/<%= card.category %>" class="back-link"><i
                class="fas fa-chevron-left me-2 mb-2"></i>Zpět na kategorii</a></li>
          <li>
            <p class="m-0"><small>
                <%= sectionName %>
            </p></small>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <main class="container mt-md-5 p-4" id="main-container">
      <div class="row">

        <!--PROGRESS STATUS MOBILE-->
        <div class="col-lg-2 mb-3 zobrazovat-jen-na-mobilu">
          <div class="card d-flex flex-row justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <div class="card-body text-center ">
              <p class="text-muted text-smaller mb-1">Karta <span id="progressCardNumMobile"><%= nextNum - 1 %></span> z <%= sectionLength %>
              </p>
              <div class="progress">
                <% if(progressStatus && progressStatus===0){ %>
                  <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar"></div>
                  <% } else { %>
                    <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar" style="width:<%= progressStatus %>%" id="progressBarMobile">
                      <span id="progressBarStatusMobile"><%= progressStatus %>%</span>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="star-at-top">
              <% if(currentUser && currentUser.isPremium){%>
                <% if(isCardSaved){%>
                  <div id="save-star-div-rendered-top" name="<%= currentUser.email %>/<%=card._id%>" class="save-star clicked" style="cursor:pointer"><i class="fas fa-star fa-lg"></i></div>
                <% } else { %>
                  <div id="save-star-div-rendered-top" name="<%= currentUser.email %>/<%=card._id%>" class="save-star" style="cursor:pointer"><i class="far fa-star fa-lg"></i></div>
                <% } %>
              <% } else if (currentUser && !currentUser.isPremium) { %>
              <div id="" class="save-star" style="cursor:pointer"><a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#savePremium"><i class="far fa-star fa-lg"></i></a></div>
              <% } else { %>
                <div style="width:14px"></div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <!--FLIPCARD-->
        <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-2 mb-3">
          <div class="flip-card" id="flip-card">
            <div class="border-grey flip-card-inner">
<              <div class="card-body flip-card-front pb-0">
                <p>Euismod lacinia at quis risus sed vulputate odio ut. Sapien eget mi proin sed libero. Sit amet nisl purus in. Eu sem integer vitae justo. Tincidunt tortor aliquam nulla facilisi cras fermentum odio eu feugiat. Neque gravida in fermentum et sollicitudin ac orci. In nibh mauris cursus mattis. Ut enim blandit volutpat maecenas. Dolor purus non enim praesent elementum. Quam id leo in vitae turpis massa sed. Id interdum velit laoreet id donec ultrices tincidunt arcu non. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada. Interdum velit euismod in pellentesque. Fringilla phasellus faucibus scelerisque eleifend donec pretium vulputate sapien. Arcu felis bibendum ut tristique et egestas. Nec ullamcorper sit amet risus nullam eget felis eget nunc. Pretium vulputate sapien nec sagittis aliquam malesuada bibendum arcu. Ultrices vitae auctor eu augue ut.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body flip-card-back pb-0">
                
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Consequat nisl vel pretium lectus quam. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!--PROGRESS STATUS PC-->
        <div class="col-lg-2 mb-3 mt-5 mt-lg-0 nezobrazovat-na-mobilu">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
              <p class="text-muted text-smaller">Karta <span id="progressCardNumMac"><%= nextNum - 1 %></span> z <%= sectionLength %>
              </p>
              <div class="progress mb-2">
                <% if(progressStatus && progressStatus===0){ %>
                  <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar"></div>
                  <% } else { %>
                    <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar" style="width:<%= progressStatus %>%" id="progressBarMac">
                      <span id="progressBarStatusMac"><%= progressStatus %>%</span>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-2">
          <div class="text-center mt-4 servis-btns d-flex justify-content-around align-items-center">
            <% if (currentUser && currentUser.admin) { %>
              <a href="/cards/edit/<%= card._id%>" class="text-muted">Upravit kartu</a>
              <a href="/cards/remove/<%= card._id%>" class="text-muted mx-3">Odstranit kartu</a>
              <% } %>
                <p id="predchozi-karticka-link" name="/category/<%= card.category %>/section/<%= card.section %>/cardAjax/<%= 0 %>" class="text-muted px-3 mb-0">Předchozí kartička</p>
                <a href="/cards/report/<%= card._id%>" target="_blank" class="text-muted px-3">Nahlásit chybu</a>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0 px-3 nezobrazovat-na-mobilu">Otáčej [mezerníkem]</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- MODAL - Saving is Premium feature info -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="savePremium" tabindex="-1">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body" style="text-align: center;">
            <h5 class="modal-title mb-3" style="text-align: center;"><i class="far fa-star fa-lg"></i> Vyzkoušej ukládání kartiček</h5>
            <p class="p-3">Hvězdičkou si můžeš <b>ukládat</b> kartičky, které si potřebuješ více zopakovat. Poté si je můžeš <b>procházet</b> pod odkazem "Uložené kartičky" v horním menu.</p>
            <p class="pb-3 px-3">Tohle a další stovky kartiček získáš <b>s předplatným Premium</b>.</p>
            <a href="/premium" class="btn btn-danger">Zjistit více</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
      <!-- JS for Bootstrap -->
      <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c9f8e59b45.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.10.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-7+zCNj/IqJ95wo16oMtfsKbZ9ccEh31eOz1HGyDuCQ6wgnyJNSYdrPa03rtR1zdB"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-QJHtvGhmr9XOIpI6YVutG+2QOK9T+ZnN4kzFN1RtK3zEFEIsxhlmWl5/YESvpZ13"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
      <script src="/js/card.js?h"></script>
</body>

</html>